Revision: 11
Description: Generator of high-energy physics events
BuildDependsOnly: true
GCC: 4.0

BuildDepends: fink (>= 0.24.12)
Depends:  %n-shlibs (=%v-%r)

Source: http://home.thep.lu.se/~torbjorn/pythia8/pythia8185.tgz
